WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.000
Benefits of using FRDR

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:11.000
By submitting your data to FRDR, you benefit from a platform designed to support both researchers and institutions.

00:00:11.000 --> 00:00:14.000
Here's what FRDR offers.

00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:22.000
Long-term preservation, accessibility, and usability of datasets, thanks to a dedicated curation and preservation team.

00:00:23.000 --> 00:00:30.000
Support for meeting funder requirements, including those related to open access and the creation of research data management plans.

00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:38.000
The ability to host large datasets, making FRDR ideal for data intensive projects that may exceed the limits of other platforms.

00:00:39.000 --> 00:00:47.000
Expert guidance on data management best practices to help make your dataset more fair, findable, accessible, interoperable, and reusable.

00:00:47.000 --> 00:00:56.000
FRDR staff work directly with researchers to ensure the data are well structured, properly documented, and ready for discovery and reuse.

